afff}</style><span data-colorid=3D"kis532geqt">SDLC Orchestrator =E2=80=94 =
Access and Testing </span></p>
<p local-id=3D"74c2b64ac148">This document provides step-by-step instructio=
ns to test the deployed SDLC Orchestrator.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6d59969a526f"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"k3ibi7598w">Tabl=
e of Contents</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"416be7f285aa">1. Prerequisites &amp; Environment Setup</p>
<p local-id=3D"9809a42c57bb">2. Developer Login (SSO Bypass)</p>
<p local-id=3D"c5586c0ef43d">3. Project Creation / Selection</p>
<p local-id=3D"8ec4658c70b2">4. PM Agent =E2=80=94 BRD Generation from Tran=
script</p>
<p local-id=3D"59a6b5e9c73d">5. PM Agent =E2=80=94 Editing the Generated BR=
D</p>
<p local-id=3D"827ee6c01cde">6. PM Agent =E2=80=94 Push BRD to Confluence &=
amp; Download</p>
<p local-id=3D"cad179db619d">7. Confluence Tab =E2=80=94 View Generated BRD=
s</p>
<p local-id=3D"8ae67a6f17e2">8. Generate Jira Stories / Epics from BRD</p>
<p local-id=3D"4e73b0a35150">9. Jira Tab =E2=80=94 View &amp; Push Stories =
to Jira</p>
<p local-id=3D"932d9b8bc452">10. Orchestrator Agent =E2=80=94 Knowledge Bas=
e Chat</p>
<p local-id=3D"6cd38978dba6">11. Analyst Agent =E2=80=94 BRD Generation</p>
<p local-id=3D"0f7de0ec3935">12. Automated Sync (Confluence =E2=86=94 Jira =
=E2=86=94 Orchestrator)</p>
<p local-id=3D"6918f57ed17e"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"dkkmhsdkpb">1. P=
rerequisites &amp; Environment Setup</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c498ad9cd120">Before testing, ensure the following are in pl=
ace:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a12376aff045">
<li local-id=3D"6fab597b2fb6">
<p local-id=3D"fca8fe7b343d">Deployed URL is accessible (<a class=3D"extern=
al-link" href=3D"https://sdlc-dev.deluxe.com/" rel=3D"nofollow">https://sdl=
c-dev.deluxe.com/</a>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae7513956fe6">
<p local-id=3D"535927cf9886">Test transcript files ready (.txt, .docx, and/=
or .pdf format)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"41f18f1a839d"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"mk4qsi8tty">1.1 =
Connecting to Atlassian</span></strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"55ec17a6-71ef-4faa-afe3-eb7d890447c3">
<li local-id=3D"b6b3ef86-485c-45f5-9077-1b03750549a5">
<p local-id=3D"9bb782016c37">Visit this URL: <a class=3D"external-link" hre=
f=3D"https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens" rel=3D"no=
follow">Atlassian account | security | api tokens</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e899c77aa30e">
<p local-id=3D"da8e7146cacc">Click the create API token button on top.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"96b8db6a1756"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260327-073235.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"38419fe5a40424c476d138f1a60b29d10eb16256bb=
