ght=3D"306"></span>
<p local-id=3D"35be43e6e5ba">Once the Key is generated, <strong>copy it</st=
rong>. This is important because <strong>the keys can=E2=80=99t be viewed a=
gain</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d770f500ced9">
<p local-id=3D"49bc49d65bd8">Click on Link Atlassian Account in SDLC Orches=
trator</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b109f1ec29de"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
