<p local-id=3D"299efe89feff"></p>
<p local-id=3D"b524ee20d077"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"v3z66803v3">4. P=
M Agent =E2=80=94 BRD Generation from Transcript</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"467583922244">The PM Agent generates a Business Requirements=
 Document (BRD) from uploaded meeting transcripts. It supports .txt, .docx,=
 and .pdf files. Multiple files can be uploaded simultaneously and their co=
ntent will be concatenated.</p>
<p local-id=3D"833f79a0d8f4"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Open the project you =
created (or any existing project).</p>
<p local-id=3D"de422a4bd0e7"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Navigate to the "PM A=
gent" or "BRD Generation" tab/section.</p>
<p local-id=3D"88c3570dab1f"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Click the "Upload Tra=
nscript" button or drag-and-drop files into the upload area.</p>
<p local-id=3D"37a7b6fabd3b"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Select one or more tr=
anscript files:</p>
<p local-id=3D"2692b3040579" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">=E2=80=A2 Suppo=
rted formats: .txt, .docx, .pdf<br>
=E2=80=A2 You can select multiple files at once<br>
=E2=80=A2 Files will be listed in the upload area for review before submiss=
ion</p>
<p local-id=3D"eb88f712a177"><strong>Step 5: </strong>Click "Generate BRD" =
(or "Submit") to start the generation process.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c50e6aca3a55"><strong>Step 6: </strong>Wait for the BRD gene=
ration to complete.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2bd3174ee00b" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">This typically =
takes 30=E2=80=9390 seconds depending on transcript length. A loading indic=
ator should be visible during processing.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b0549eff023b"><strong>Step 7: </strong>Review the generated =
BRD displayed on screen.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5f464fe4e0e8"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>A complete BRD is generated with sectio=
ns such as: Executive Summary, Project Scope, Functional Requirements, Non-=
Functional Requirements, Assumptions &amp; Constraints, etc. The content sh=
ould be derived from the uploaded transcript(s).</p>
<p local-id=3D"560dbab3d50d"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"lhtz26bi34">Note=
: </span></strong>If multiple files were uploaded, verify that content from=
 ALL files is reflected in the generated BRD, not just the first file.</p><=
span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluenc=
e-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-left"=
 width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"cb1ac65dbc918ad701810cfa8b471256473a=
cb50fdd0a71480dc12aec349be03" data-image-src=3D"https://deluxe.atlassian.ne=
