le" height=3D"222"></span>
<p local-id=3D"9bce068a4f08"></p>
<p local-id=3D"383c22d4f0f3"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"o88r1eci7t">5. P=
M Agent =E2=80=94 Editing the Generated BRD</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"5d39afce5d87">After BRD generation, users can edit individua=
l sections or the entire BRD.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3faec1c4f54e"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"j83cejtazd">5a. =
Section-wise Editing</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c96163a14c98"><strong>Step 1: </strong>In the generated BRD =
view, click on a specific section heading (e.g., 'Stakeholders').</p>
<p local-id=3D"1af66a966ba5"><strong>Step 2: </strong>The content of the se=
ction shoudl appear in chatbox</p>
<p local-id=3D"1017f2317765"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Modify the content =
=E2=80=94 add, remove, or rephrase text.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ef6faf9433e4"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>The section is updated with your change=
s. Other sections remain unchanged.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-f=
ile-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-left" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" sr=
c=3D"094ec972e74a023ad209ede162d96e9d91389a234bb05ff35235f6a17fd56659" data=
