<p local-id=3D"697415b6f004"></p>
<p local-id=3D"56e3c1e0e98e"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"c5x0fljjdo">5b. =
Full BRD Editing</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"addf2755ed3b"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Click "View Full BRD"=
 to see the complete document.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ac382de0af28"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Make edits across BRD=
 by providing prompt</p>
<p local-id=3D"36dc319bcd8e"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>All changes are persisted. Refreshing t=
he page should show the updated BRD.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-=
file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
