<p local-id=3D"0b76329af22f"></p>
<p local-id=3D"e3145d736dd9"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"uf00s9vv3u">6. P=
M Agent =E2=80=94 Push BRD to Confluence &amp; Download</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"1e7b2673b1d2"><strong>Step 1: </strong>In the BRD view, clic=
k "Push to Confluence".</p>
<p local-id=3D"38b69cdfb714"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Confirm the target Co=
nfluence space (should default to the project's linked space).</p>
<p local-id=3D"952de8064fd2"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Wait for the push to =
complete. Orchestrator will redirect to the created Confluence page.</p>
<p local-id=3D"91d622504373"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>The BRD is now available as a Confluenc=
e page in the linked space.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a6d76c82c05d"><strong>Step 4: </strong>(Optional) Click "Dow=
nload as DOCX" to download the BRD as a Word document.</p>
<p local-id=3D"65b51f4dee66"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>A .docx file is downloaded containing t=
he full BRD content with proper formatting.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2adf0680c8bd"></p>
<p local-id=3D"3842aa0dd6b7"></p>
<p local-id=3D"726ed0164b1a"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"yqj7r3gv75">7. C=
onfluence Tab =E2=80=94 View Generated BRDs</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d576e8d8c8ff"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Navigate to the "Conf=
luence" tab within the project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"95ca6b1da22b"><strong>Step 2: </strong>You should see a list=
 of BRDs that have been pushed to Confluence.</p>
<p local-id=3D"64255cea6ead"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Click on a BRD to vie=
w its content.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1be55e3db407"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Verify the content ma=
tches what was generated and edited in the PM Agent.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f7cd6a6f1fd4"><strong>Step 5</strong>: Any changes made in C=
onfluence page will be refected in the Confluence tab inside the Orchestrat=
or.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9b52f85b058d"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>All pushed BRDs are listed. Clicking on=
 one shows its full content. Content matches the latest version from the PM=
 Agent.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapp=
er confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image=
 image-left" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"e2dc675c9209958e266c0d7d=
