<p local-id=3D"14ab5bad5233"></p>
<p local-id=3D"43edb83cc36d"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"t6od5mcvu6">8. G=
enerate Jira Stories / Epics from BRD</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"4858f86e9db9"><strong>Step 1: </strong>From the Confluence t=
ab, select a BRD and click "Generate Jira Stories".</p>
<p local-id=3D"6834091ddf8b"><strong>Step 2: </strong>The system will analy=
ze the BRD and generate Epics and User Stories.</p>
<p local-id=3D"91290e453ddd"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Wait for generation t=
o complete (this may take 30=E2=80=9360 seconds).</p>
<p local-id=3D"08651a5d556a"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Review the generated =
Epics and Stories:</p>
<p local-id=3D"1ad7d13d02cf" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">=E2=80=A2 Each =
Epic should represent a major feature area from the BRD<br>
=E2=80=A2 Stories should be broken down under their respective Epics<br>
=E2=80=A2 Each Story should have a title, description, and acceptance crite=
ria</p>
<p local-id=3D"e603c62d5774"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>Epics and Stories are generated that al=
ign with the BRD content. The structure is logical and covers the major req=
uirements from the BRD.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec5cededb2f2"><strong>Step 5: </strong>Click "Push to Jira" =
to push the stories to the linked Jira project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f93a9035491e"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>Stories are pushed to Jira successfully=
. A confirmation message is shown. The stories should appear in the linked =
Jira project with correct Epic links, descriptions, and acceptance criteria=
.</p>
<p local-id=3D"af6df3bdef12"><strong>Step 6: </strong>Verify in Jira: Open =
the linked Jira project and confirm the stories exist.</p>
<p local-id=3D"23e3a720dd73"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"mpfe9jbedo">Note=
: </span></strong>If push fails, check that the backend has valid Jira API =
credentials and that the target Jira project allows issue creation.<br></p>=
<span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluen=
ce-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-left=
" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"3fad6432dac6dc92e7a27d44e3162242d52=
