<p local-id=3D"0982a4d85a2d"></p>
<p local-id=3D"0be4d96283b5"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"qm41j294ir">9. O=
rchestrator Home Page =E2=80=94 Knowledge Base Chat</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"6b0473464fc6">The Orchestrator Home Page uses RAG (Retrieval=
-Augmented Generation) to answer questions based on synced Confluence and J=
ira content for the project.</p>
<p local-id=3D"70c4f4db359d"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Navigate to Home Page=
.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9a1e8336b6fd"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Ensure the project ha=
s synced data (If you have edited or created new confluence pages or jira s=
tories or epics).</p>
<p local-id=3D"a3059e21eec2" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">If not synced, =
click 'Sync Docs' and wait for the sync to complete.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c0e0e95517d5"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Type a question in th=
e chat input related to the project's Confluence/Jira content.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ac2021607452" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">Example: 'What =
are the main requirements for the authentication module?'</p>
<p local-id=3D"427644aca13f"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Submit the query and =
wait for the response.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5d352f9253d4"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>The Agent returns a relevant answer bas=
ed on the synced knowledge base. Sources (Confluence pages or Jira issues) =
are cited in the response.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cda11fcaf30d"><strong>Step 5: </strong>Verify source citatio=
ns =E2=80=94 click on source links to confirm they point to real Confluence=
 pages or Jira issues.</p>
<p local-id=3D"068f00a10fb4"><strong>Step 6: </strong>Ask follow-up questio=
ns to test the conversational context.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1168b984245b"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"mxzyyqtxas">Note=
: </span></strong>The quality of answers depends on the synced content. If =
answers seem incomplete, try syncing docs again to pull the latest content.=
</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper conf=
luence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-=
