<p local-id=3D"3139e14f86ad"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"n2joy5mexe">11. =
Analyst Agent =E2=80=94 BRD Generation</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"75eb5f1b8e3d">The Analyst Agent can also generate BRDs, but =
instead of using uploaded transcripts, it uses the chat conversation with U=
ser as a context to generate teh BRD.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9d9138ae3aca"><strong>Step 1: </strong>In the Analyst Agent =
section, have a chat with Analyst agent to discuss about the project .</p>
<p local-id=3D"1f03fa9506a3"><strong>Step 2</strong>: The analyst agent ask=
s intelligent questions regarding the project. <br><strong>Step 3: </strong=
>Click on "Generate BRD" and wait for BRD generation (30=E2=80=9390 seconds=
).</p>
<p local-id=3D"dad6ce829fb1"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Review the generated =
BRD.</p>
<p local-id=3D"08d2f0b2d5bf"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>A BRD is generated using context from C=
hat. The BRD shoudl have different tags such as "User - Provided " or "AI -=
 Assumption" to clearly mark the difference between the content provided by=
 user and generated by AI.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conflu=
ence-embedded-image image-left" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"b1e9a=
06d63a4d65baf2ce4787398e90ae6b1ed115b01d2f488c3a430f66e22a2" data-image-src=
=3D"https://deluxe.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/8254423056/att_9=
_for_8254423056.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774506745243&amp;ca=
cheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"748" data-width=3D"1858" data-u=
nresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"8254423116" data-l=
inked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-=
linked-resource-default-alias=3D"att_9_for_8254423056.png" data-base-url=3D=
"https://deluxe.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"im=
age/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"8254423056" data-linked-resou=
rce-container-version=3D"4" data-media-id=3D"ef4e2171-4d01-4d7e-af98-5690b3=
505d1d" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"188"></span>
<p local-id=3D"1b6eb2fc1548"></p>
<p local-id=3D"81f4c650c657"><strong><span data-colorid=3D"frct0qjbwg">12. =
Automated Sync (Confluence / Jira / Orchestrator)</span></strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"c2ddd917ea2a">The platform supports incremental sync between=
 Confluence, Jira, and the orchestrator's vector store. This keeps the Orch=
estrator's knowledge base up to date.</p>
<p local-id=3D"876a0c95d727"><strong>Step 1: </strong>Click "Sync Docs" in =
the project view.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c27a0c92cd0d"><strong>Step 2: </strong>The system triggers a=
n incremental sync:</p>
<p local-id=3D"bd7d332d4aab" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">=E2=80=A2 Fetch=
es changed Confluence pages since last sync<br>
=E2=80=A2 Fetches changed Jira issues since last sync<br>
=E2=80=A2 Updates embeddings in the vector store</p>
<p local-id=3D"94978ba2bb87"><strong>Step 3: </strong>Wait for the sync to =
complete. A status indicator should show progress.</p>
<p local-id=3D"498baee7fc76"><strong>Step 4: </strong>Verify sync results:<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"4c99a5fbb540" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">=E2=80=A2 Check=
 the sync status shows updated counts<br>
=E2=80=A2 Ask the Analyst Agent about recently added/changed content<br>
=E2=80=A2 Confirm new content is reflected in responses</p>
<p local-id=3D"08c6c92d9078"><strong><span class=3D"legacy-color-text-green=
2">Expected Result: </span></strong>Sync completes successfully. New or mod=
ified Confluence pages and Jira issues are reflected in the Analyst Agent's=
 responses.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-w=
rapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-i=
mage image-left" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"0b880a43e0fc35c62f63=
dc65f5fdafa370bac65820d4f7f441894e40eda702fc" data-image-src=3D"https://del=
